ğŸ§© Import in Python
```python

from encodream.core import *

ascii_art("PYTHON")

utf8_encode("hello")        # b'hello'
string_to_binary("abc")     # '01100001 01100010 01100011'
machine_code_dump("Hi!")    # '48 69 21'

plot_string_bytes("ASCII")
display_ascii_table("arduino")
```

